@startuml C2_Register_ShippingAgents_Logical_View
title C2 – Port Logistics Management System (PLMS) – Logical Container View (Shipping Agents)

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
  FontStyle bold
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor Wheat
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor LightGray
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor CornflowerBlue
  FontColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

' === Atores Externos ===
actor "Organization Representative" as Representative
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer

' === Sistema Externo ===
cloud "External IAM Provider\n(SSO / OAuth 2.0)" as IAM

' === Sistema em foco ===
rectangle "Port Logistics Management System (PLMS)" as PLMS {
  rectangle "Frontend Web Application\n(React / Angular)" as Frontend
  rectangle "Shipping Agents Management API\n(ASP.NET Core Web API)" as API
  database "PLMS Database\n(SQL / EF Core)" as DB
}

' === Relações ===
Representative --> Frontend : Submete registo (HTTPS)
Officer --> Frontend : Consulta e valida organizações
Frontend --> API : Chamadas REST (JSON)
API --> DB : Operações CRUD (Entity Framework Core)
API --> IAM : Autenticação e Autorização

@enduml
